'''Novi学区'''（'''{{lang|en|Novi Community School District}}'''）是一个美国[[密歇根|密歇根]]县的学区，总部在{{link-en|诺维|Novi, Michigan}}教育服务大楼(Educational Services Building)。<ref>"[http://www.novi.k12.mi.us/downloads/esl_docs/volunteer_letter-simplifiedchinese-2014_20140728_113300_1.pdf Volunteer Letter (Chinese)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.novi.k12.mi.us/downloads/esl_docs/volunteer_letter-simplifiedchinese-2014_20140728_113300_1.pdf |date=20141120060815 }}" (). Novi学区. "或直接寄至“教育服务大楼”(Educational Services Building)，收件人是HumanResources，地址是25345 Taft Road, Novi, MI 48374。"</ref>

Novi学区营运5间小学、1间初中、和1间高中、<ref>"[http://www.novi.k12.mi.us/ Home] {{Wayback|url=http://www.novi.k12.mi.us/ |date=20141129035527 }}." Novi学区.</ref> 2010年12月学生人数达左右6,300人 2011年3月日本学生人与美国日本学生人数达多于1,700人。<ref name="Earthquake">"[http://detroit.cbslocal.com/2011/03/11/novi-area-home-to-many-affected-by-earthquake-in-japan/ Novi Area Home To Many Affected By Earthquake In Japan] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Fm3lTEwk?url=http://detroit.cbslocal.com/2011/03/11/novi-area-home-to-many-affected-by-earthquake-in-japan/ |date=20130410115153 |dateformat=iso }}." () {{link-en|WWJ-TV|WWJ-TV}}. March 11, 2011. Retrieved on April 13, 2011.</ref>

